  "description": "REFINED UNIFIED MODEL: Transport with spherical scattering kernel. Tests the hypothesis that 274 Mpc (geometric fit) = 2 \u00d7 137 Mpc (radius). Includes proper \u2113(\u2113+1)/(2\u03c0) normalization and spectral tilt. This should match the geometric model's fit quality while revealing transport physics.",
  "experiment_id": "exp_2025_cmb_unified_refined",
